Dear Mr. Jordan,

I hope this email finds you well. I am writing to provide a freight quote for the shipment of 4701MT of sugar from Changzhou to St Helier.

We are pleased to offer the vessel FLEX ENDEAVOUR for this voyage. The initial freight quote is USD83.47 per metric ton on a CIF basis.

Please let me know if you have any questions or need further clarifications.

Best regards,
Andrea Butler
Anderson Shipping Brokers

email_chain.subject: Re: Freight Quote for Sugar Shipment from Changzhou to St Helier
email_chain.body:
Dear Andrea,

Thank you for the quote. However, I must point out that the route from Changzhou to St Helier is quite short. Given the minimal transit time, we were expecting a proportionally lower freight rate.

Could you please review the quote and provide a revised rate? Additionally, could you confirm the laycan and the demurrage rate per day?

Best regards,
Lee Jordan
Chartering Co.

email_chain.subject: Re: Freight Quote for Sugar Shipment from Changzhou to St Helier - Revised
email_chain.body:
Dear Mr. Jordan,

Thank you for your feedback. We understand your concern regarding the short voyage. After reviewing the details, we are able to offer a revised freight rate of USD78.95 per metric ton on a CIF basis.

The laycan for this voyage is expected to start on 15/07/2013 and end on 20/07/2013. The demurrage rate is set at us$20,000 per day.

Please confirm if this revised rate is acceptable, and let us know if you need any further information.

Best regards,
Andrea Butler
Anderson Shipping Brokers

email_chain.subject: Re: Freight Quote for Sugar Shipment from Changzhou to St Helier - Confirmation
email_chain.body:
Dear Andrea,

Thank you for the revised quote. The new rate of USD78.95 per metric ton is acceptable. We also confirm the laycan dates and the demurrage rate.

We look forward to a successful voyage and future collaborations.

Best regards,
Lee Jordan
Chartering Co.
